\begin_inset Formula $\recResp$
\end_inset

 contains the sensor responses, the rows of the matrix 
\begin_inset Formula $\sensorMat$
\end_inset

 are the sensor spectral responsivities, and 
\begin_inset Formula $\illvec$
\end_inset

 is the illuminant spectral power distribution.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

