\begin_inset Formula $\illvec \approx \illBasis \illCoef$
\end_inset

. This reduces the equation to 
\begin_inset Formula \begin{equation}
\label{e8:dayEst2}
\recResp \approx (\sensorMat \illBasis) \illCoef .
\end{equation}
\end_inset

