\begin_inset Formula $3 \times 3$
\end_inset

, and its entries are all known. The sensor responses, 
\begin_inset Formula $\recResp$
\end_inset

, are also known. The only unknown is 
\begin_inset Formula $\illCoef$
\end_inset

